text: Gerola Lindahl (born 20 July 1943) is a Swedish gymnast. She competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics and the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Sweden Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
